n\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uvz1665702733910.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uvz1665702733910.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uvz1665702733910.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uvz1665702733910\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      SLE Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__sle_connector_options_171620\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can assign connector options by setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SLE_PARAMS</span> in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__topic_d58475e1_d58476e1_d58477e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__p_d58478e1_d58479e1_d58480e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SLE_PARAMS</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n            n}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__topic_d38712e1_d38713e1_d38714e1_d38715e1_d38716e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1182167e74\">\n                        \n Options\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__li_d26336e1_d26337e1_d26338e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__p_d58484e1_d58485e1_d58486e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lca1665702725226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lca1665702725226.html\" title=\"Enable or disable testing for the existence of tables and stored procedures.\">checks</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__li_d26339e1_d26340e1_d26341e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__p_d58487e1_d58488e1_d58489e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bsx1723125799922.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bsx1723125799922.html\" title=\"If the database file does not yet exist, creates a database file in the path specified by the connector setting.\">create db</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__li_d26342e1_d26343e1_d26344e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__p_d58490e1_d58491e1_d58492e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fug1665702705112.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fug1665702705112.html\" title=\"Set the default locking strategy employed by Uniface.\">default locking</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__li_d26345e1_d26346e1_d26347e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__p_d58493e1_d58494e1_d58495e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vip1665702725886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vip1665702725886.html\" title=\"Enable all characters to be used in an object or field, including diacritical signs.\">identifiers</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__li_d26348e1_d26349e1_d26350e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__p_d58496e1_d58497e1_d58498e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xie1665702706126.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xie1665702706126.html\" title=\"Set the period a database operation will wait for a database lock to be released.\">maxlockwait</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__li_d26351e1_d26352e1_d26353e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__p_d58499e1_d58500e1_d58501e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"exm1665702661663.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exm1665702661663.html\" title=\"Set the number of rows the connector selects from the DBMS in each step of the Uniface stepped hitlist.\">step size</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__topic_d38717e1_d38718e1_d38719e1_d38720e1_d38721e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1182167e162\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__p_d58505e1_d58506e1_d58507e1\">Each assignment can be no longer than one line in the assignment file. For all options, the default action is used by the connector unless specifically overridden by using the appropriate parameter.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uvz1665702733910__p_d58508e1_d58509e1_d58510e1\">All options have the form <var class=\"keyword varname\">Directive</var> = <var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>. Instead of the equal sign (=), a colon can be used. Multiple settings can be concatenated by comma-separating options. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[DRIVER_SETTINGS]\nUSYS$SLE_PARAMS = default locking: cautious, step size = off</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/msq1665702542189.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[DRIVER_SETTINGS]</a><p>Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532869\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532869\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SLE Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 SLE Connector Options You can assign connector options by setting USYS$SLE_PARAMS in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. USYS$SLE_PARAMS Option { , Option n} Options checks create db default locking identifiers maxlockwait step size Description Each assignment can be no longer than one line in the assignment file. For all options, the default action is used by the connector unless specifically overridden by using the appropriate parameter. All options have the form Directive = Value . Instead of the equal sign (=), a colon can be used. Multiple settings can be concatenated by comma-separating options. For example: [DRIVER_SETTINGS] USYS$SLE_PARAMS = default locking: cautious, step size = off Copy Related Links [DRIVER_SETTINGS] Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}